# Decision demo (synthetic) - exercises if / jump / directional sensing.
# Worker at x=2. West neighbour is a data cube, so the "if w == datacube" branch
# runs: step west onto the cube, then west again into the hole -> exit.
# (Not the real Year 05 grid; a self-consistent test of control flow.)
name Decision Demo
dim 5 1
row O1@.O
goal all_exited
